Insert and display collections to your Lightning pages using the CRM Analytics Collection component.

Available in: Lightning Experience, Essentials, Group, Enterprise, Professional, Unlimited, and Developer Editions.
Also available with CRM Analytics.

To add a collection to a Lightning page:
Use CRM Analytics
Drag the CRM Analytics Collection component to the canvas.
Select an available collection from the Collection lookup.
Save the page when finished.
title: Adding Collections to Lightning Pages
